Fri Apr 17 12:00:00 UTC 2026 - Alessio Biancalana <dottorblaster@opensuse.org>

- Initial package of cpptrace 1.0.4.
  Simple, portable, drop-in C++ stacktrace library, using libdwarf
  for symbol resolution and libunwind for stack unwinding.
- Split into libcpptrace1 (shared library) and cpptrace-devel
  (headers, pkg-config data, CMake config files) per the openSUSE
  Shared Library Packaging Policy.

